Package: pollimetry
Type: Package
Title: Tools to estimate pollinator body size and foraging distance
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-02-20
Author: c(Authors@R: person("Liam", "Kendall", email = "liam.k.kendall@gmail.com",role=c("aut","cre"),
                     person("Ignasi","Bartomeus", email = "nacho.bartomeus@gmail.com",role="aut"))

Description: Tools to estimate pollinator body size and foraging distance. This package combines novel (described i Knendall et al. XXXXX) as well pre-existing predictive allometries for pollinator body size and foraging distance.
Pre-existing equations are implemented for a variety of Diptera, Lepidoptera and Hymenoptera taxa.

Depends:
  R (>= 3.0.0)
